Package common

Class Visit

java.lang.Object
common.Visit
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Visit extends Object implements Serializable
The Visit class represents a visit made by a traveler to a park. It contains information about the visit date, entering time, exiting time, park number, and order ID.
